Privacy Policy for Bilkent Cafeteria Menu App

At Bilkent Cafeteria Menu, we respect and value the privacy of our users. We do not collect any personal information from our users, except for their favorite courses. We do not associate this information with any user data, and we do not share any information with third parties.

We may share the list of most demanded courses on public media, but this will be done anonymously and without revealing any user-specific information.

We do not use any tracking or analytics tools, and we do not display any ads in our app. We only provide cafeteria menu information for our users to access and enjoy.

Data Sharing and Security:

Since we do not collect any personal information from our users, there is no data sharing or security concern.

Updates to Our Privacy Policy:

If we decide to change our Privacy Policy in the future, we will update this page.

Contact Us:

If you have any questions or concerns regarding our app or privacy policy, please contact us at mustafa@altinisik.net.
